	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have a bunch of AT29C040 that work great. I think 29F040 is good too.
<br />
<br />BTW, if you want to program EPROMs, you have to check if the programmer has input for an AC adapter, because the 5V supplied by USB are not enough for programming EPROMs.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


